title: Better MVE functions
body:
* Changed make_block to return a data frame.
* Changed make_block to return desired result when tau > 1.
* Changed multiview to shift target_column if it is numeric.
* Changed multiview to handle string target_column.
* Added tests to test the changes to make_block.
* Made forecast_machine.cpp complain when prediction variance is zero

title: Simplify compute_stats
body:
Rcpp can implicitly convert NumericVectors to vectors of doubles, so one tweak to the input arguments for `compute_stats` and two assignments and SLOCs go away. It also requires renaming an ambiguous function which I think is mostly an argument for not leaving multiple functions around with the same name unless you're explicitly inlining ;)

(is there any reason RcppEigen isn't used, and precompiled Eigen objects are preferred/)
